scoringPlays.text: Jalen Hurts 27 Yd Run (Andy Pappanastos Kick)
Calvin Ridley 78 Yd pass from Jalen Hurts (Andy Pappanastos Kick)
Warren Jackson 4 Yd pass from Nick Stevens (Wyatt Bryan Kick)
Robert Foster 52 Yd pass from Jalen Hurts (Andy Pappanastos Kick)
Bo Scarbrough 9 Yd Run (Andy Pappanastos Kick)
Damien Harris 5 Yd Run (Andy Pappanastos Kick)
Nick Stevens 5 Yd Run (Wyatt Bryan Kick)

videos.description: Alabama quarterback Jalen Hurts scrambles and runs all the way to the end zone on the 27-yard TD.
videos.headline: Hurts takes it himself for Alabama TD

videos.description: Off the play-action Jalen Hurts throws to Calvin Ridley on the slant who takes it 78-yards for the Alabama TD.
videos.headline: Hurts connects with Ridley for 78-yard TD

videos.description: Nick Stevens finds Michael Gallup on the sideline who makes defenders miss for a 39-yard gain for Colorado State
videos.headline: Colorado State moves into Alabama territory

videos.description: Rams QB Nick Stevens throws the corner fade to Warren Jackson who reaches over the Alabama defender for the TD.
videos.headline: Colorado State's Jackson goes over the back for the TD

videos.description: Jalen Hurts finds  Robert Foster on the sideline who turns it upfield and scores on the 52-yard TD.
videos.headline: Alabama scores from midfield on Foster TD

videos.description: Alabama head coach Nick Saban talks about how his defense performed in the 1st half including a few big plays the let up.
videos.headline: Saban says Alabama not making plays when they need to

videos.description: Alabama DB Ronnie Harrison intercepts the pass from Colorado State QB Nick Stevens off a deflection.
videos.headline: Alabama picks off pass on deflection

videos.description: Alabama RB Bo Scarbrough rushes up the middle and brushes off defenders for the 9-yard TD.
videos.headline: Scarbrough powers his way in for another Crimson Tide TD

videos.description: Alabama CB Hootie Jones easily picks off the overthrown pass from Nick Stevens and returns it to the Colorado State 11-yard line.
videos.headline: Alabama almost returns another INT

videos.description: RB Damien Harris reaches into the end zone to add onto the Crimson Tide lead.
videos.headline: Harris dives into the end zone

videos.description: Jalen Hurts throws for 248 yards and rushes for 103 more while accounting for three touchdowns in No. 1 Alabama's 41-23 win against Colorado State.
videos.headline: Hurts leads Alabama to victory
